eting", "bbox": [195.8, 976.6, 1112.6, 993.3]}, {"text": "segment, are now included in the Midstream segment. Comparable prior period information has been recast to reflect our revised", "bbox": [195.8, 997.5, 1112.6, 1014.1]}, {"text": "presentation. The results for the pipeline and storage assets were recast effective January 1, 2015, and the results for the terminal assets", "bbox": [195.8, 1018.3, 1112.6, 1035.0]}, {"text": "were recast effective April 1, 2016. Prior to these dates these assets were not considered businesses and therefore there are no financial", "bbox": [195.8, 1039.1, 1112.7, 1055.8]}, {"text": "results from which to recast segment results.", "bbox": [195.8, 1060.0, 492.0, 1076.6]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [162.5, 1085.2, 175.1, 1096.1]}, {"text": "Includes intersegment sales and sales destined for export.", "bbox": [195.8, 1085.0, 577.4, 1101.6]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [162.5, 1110.2, 174.5, 1121.1]}, {"text": "Sales revenue less cost of refinery inputs and purchased products, divided by total refinery throughputs. Excludes the LCM inventory", "bbox": [195.8, 1110.0, 1112.6, 1126.6]}, {"text": "valuation adjustments.", "bbox": [195.8, 1130.8, 345.7, 1147.5]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [162.5, 1156.1, 175.1, 1166.9]}, {"text": "Per barrel of total refinery throughputs.", "bbox": [195.8, 1155.8, 457.3, 1172.5]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [162.5, 1181.1, 174.5, 1191.9]}, {"text": "Includes utilities, labor, routine maintenance and other operating costs.", "bbox": [195.8, 1180.8, 667.4, 1197.5]}, {"text": "73", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}